{"tid":302254,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得呢個男人點","createTime":"2017-06-29T08:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T12:46:15.000Z","uid":125696,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e36234171d2a43fbdbb87103174d48f44fc7b9a3","tid":302254,"uid":125696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:58:23.000Z","msg":"我同呢個人係上網識, 見左幾個月, 大家互相係有好感<br />\n至到有一日睇戲, 去到氣氛岩既時候, 拖手KISS之後正常情況下都會告白啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住佢乜撚野都唔講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送到我返屋企就完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後個日我約左佢出黎當面問, 「你想我地呢段關係點發展」<br />\n佢話佢同EX有約定唔可以咁快同其他人一齊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係另一邊廂又話「好想見你」「你對我好重要架」<br />\n我心諗  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我俾左一個月時間佢諗清楚自己想點, 但係到而家都係冇撚答過我  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\np.s. 見到有巴打開左post講春光乍洩突然諗起呢個人連手機wallpaper都係呢套戲<br />\n跟住一言驚醒洛克人其實佢仲好掛住ex 係咪  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ab33df1ab4df4d23a01a7ab8622756f4c2c9f5","tid":302254,"uid":86403,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a43eab8310ce3e6d2b73ddf3f70035bd3937b3","tid":302254,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:00:11.000Z","msg":"你雞黎咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9<br />\n你以為自己係邊撚個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人當傻仔玩完攞左著數仲周圍話人知<br />\n真係蠢撚到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dae7ab615394ebf0aa583b2e5cba4e1d76bfd9","tid":302254,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0